 CheckPoint is a weekly, half-hour investigative Current Affairs show featuring thought-provoking journalism. The programme brings together a team of seasoned television producers and investigative journalists whose voices, faces and backgrounds reflect South Africa's multicultural diversity. Catch the episodes on Tuesdays at 20:30. Phone: 011 537 9300 Email: CheckPoint@enca.com Twitter: @CheckPoint_enca Facebook: CheckPoint with Nkepile Mabuse